<p>FAM Radio is a bi-yearly<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup> Podcast.<br />
<em>Episodes available on <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/foundation-after-midnight-radio-scp/id909033904?mt=2">iTunes</a>, <a href="https://soundcloud.com/scpfamradio">Soundcloud</a>, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/toadkingstudios1">Youtube</a>, <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/2u5lDr4P5MciOj7UPWdF0c">Spotify</a> and most podcast portals.</em></p>
</div>
</div>
<p>A thank you to all our listeners, all of you damn fine Foundation employees listening in from around the world. We know life within this clandestine organization can be strict, intrusive, and downright dangerous, but remember, your work in the shadows saves those who live in the light.</p>
<p>This is the only after midnight radio broadcast for the Foundation, by the Foundation. Stay tuned for site announcement, personnel notes, containment breach updates, and much, much more!</p>
<p>I’m your host, DJ Scip, and you’re listening to 93.<strong>[REDACTED]</strong> FAM radio!</p>
