<p><strong>Toadking07 Backstage Notes:</strong></p>
<p>Things were hitting the fan and I wanted to show that in the audio quality and how DJ Scip was holding up. He sighs more, he stumbles, he questions himself, he sounds tired. Wanted to make this really wear on him, even from the safety of his bunker underground.</p>
<p>We put out the call for personnel to be read as deceased on the episode and got a lot of responses. Unfortunately reading the full list would have made for a dull episode so I had to speed it up a little. My apologies to anyone who didn't make the cut, we are still thankful for your sacrifice and submission. Special thanks to Lyrahel who read most of the list only to have us cut more than half of it.</p>
