<p><span style="background-color: black; color: black">An anomalous radio host hijacks</span> the radio station, broadcasting announcements and references before being <span style="background-color: black; color: black">recontainted by a MTF team</span>. <span style="background-color: black; color: black">Connor from Confinement</span> is sent into the booth, without much success.</p>
